{"tid":1006912,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"王晶翻拍<唐伯虎點秋香2019> 陳浩文, 陳百祥, 肥仔聰, 何浩文主演","createTime":"2019-02-03T11:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T13:02:43.000Z","uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"677f947caf4e9cfed432d067b7ed33299121a604","tid":1006912,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pCoaewXKhW8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpCoaewXKhW8&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7gx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=f8d5123e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pCoaewXKhW8</a><br />\n<br />\n《唐伯虎點秋香》是一代人心目中的經典之作，原作中，多個熟悉面孔再現經典橋段，飽含致敬之意。此外影片還加入了許多新巧思，創新升級老橋段，積極順應網生代觀影口味的變化。講述了黃伯虎、劉浩南和排骨自幼就是好友，三人都是《唐伯虎點秋香》這部電影的迷弟，從小看到大，長大之後，三人通過高科技，穿越到《唐伯虎點秋香》電影中，在華府經歷了各種鬧劇，最終收穫了友情和愛情的故事。"},{"pid":"ad825ba878ecba3948821628c157cd732814818c","tid":1006912,"uid":20066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"唔好整臭我地個回憶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ec30513a6365d7a68787d850da8cd519f7f6ce","tid":1006912,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:07:37.000Z","msg":"王子涵做秋香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"460767928441eb0a7fba9e2ab68ec81ab0891caf","tid":1006912,"uid":8247,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:07:48.000Z","msg":"屌  幾年前杜生先拍完唐伯虎衝上雲霄<br />\n你又同我穿越又拍唐伯虎想點呀<br />\n真係又係你呀王生"},{"pid":"9dff823c32db6d6a6e9aecd1aa5fe7b30722e0b0","tid":1006912,"uid":232466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:08:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老味個撚個都翻炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba96d93fc79a33a97515eb9dcc9ed70f7f45205","tid":1006912,"uid":76674,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:09:11.000Z","msg":"屎尿屁玩60分鐘<br />\n賭術千術30分鐘<br />\n幾分鐘集體回憶<br />\n智商冇80都拍到"},{"p